## üìã **Maintenance Checklist**

### Before Adding New Content:
- [ ] Identify which of the 3 root domains it belongs to
- [ ] Determine if new parent concepts are needed
- [ ] Plan the Wikipedia-style linking structure
- [ ] Consider cross-references to related concepts

### After Adding New Content:
- [ ] Verify single parent tag assignment
- [ ] Add TOC structure if tiddler will have children
- [ ] Create appropriate links to related content
- [ ] Test navigation from root to new content

### Weekly Hierarchy Audit:
- [ ] List all tiddlers tagged with "TableOfContents" (should be exactly 3)
- [ ] Check for orphaned tiddlers without proper parents
- [ ] Verify TOC structure exists on all parent tiddlers
- [ ] Validate content is in appropriate hierarchy level

